## Data Flow

```
Source:
  apis/org/openmcf/provider/{provider}/{component}/v1/catalog-page.md
  apis/org/openmcf/provider/{provider}/{component}/v1/presets/*.yaml + *.md

  |  yarn copy-docs  (copy-component-docs.ts)
  v

Intermediate:
  site/public/docs/catalog/{provider}/{slug}/index.md        (with frontmatter)
  site/public/docs/catalog/{provider}/{slug}/presets/*.md
  site/public/docs/catalog/{provider}/{slug}/presets/*.yaml
  site/public/docs/catalog/{provider}/index.md               (provider index)
  site/public/docs/catalog/index.md                          (catalog index)

  |  yarn generate-structure  (generate-docs-structure.ts)
  v

Runtime data:
  site/public/docs-structure.json

  |  loaded by DocsSidebar.tsx and page.tsx at runtime
  v

Rendered:
  Sidebar (DocsSidebar.tsx)           -- uses item.title for labels
  Catalog grid (CatalogProviderGrid)  -- uses provider.title for display
  Provider index pages                -- uses PROVIDER_DISPLAY_NAMES for heading
  Component pages                     -- rendered from copied markdown
```

